Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.91,0:51:11.07,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}I remember the dream I left behind as a child
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.20,0:51:22.13,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}Faintly and sweetly singing the bright green sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.46,0:51:28.24,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}My fairy tale
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.15,0:51:39.98,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}I knew of an eternity where nothing would end
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.84,0:51:53.15,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}The two's story that nobody talks of anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.57,0:52:04.72,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}Where are you going after leaving a kiss behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.93,0:52:15.38,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}You hold a lamp and disappear into the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.50,0:52:21.67,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}In the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.81,0:52:32.88,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}There's a familiar face walking in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.12,0:52:38.73,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}Your house is far away
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.76,0:52:44.12,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}You won't be able to reach it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.41,0:52:50.99,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}Your fairy tale
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.03,0:53:21.81,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}{\an1}The eternity I saw in\Nmy dream is still closed
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.72,0:53:27.19,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}{\an3}The mistake is\Nstill deeply hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.34,0:53:29.64,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}{\an1}The return path is disappearing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.58,0:53:38.13,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}{\an3}I can't see you anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.57,0:53:42.99,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}{\an1}Good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.38,0:53:44.03,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}{\an3}Good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.72,0:53:54.71,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}Where are you going after escaping the forest of mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.05,0:54:06.19,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}You wave once and leave for tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.30,0:54:17.44,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}The eternity ends when I fall in love with you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.63,0:54:28.09,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}The happiness and pain of life starts
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.19,0:54:34.51,Translation,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(200,200)\be1\org(0,0)}In the light
